<!DOCTYPE html>

<head>
<title>Disaster Preparedness Survey</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Disaster Preparedness Survey</h1>

<form>

    <h3>Household Information</h3>

    <label>Address:</label><br>
    <input type="text" name="address" required><br><br>

    <label>Family Members:</label><br>
    <input type="number" name="family_members" min="1" required>

    <br><br>

    <h3>Preparedness Check</h3>

    <label>Emergency Kit:</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="emergency_kit" value="Yes" required> Yes<br>
    <input type="radio" name="emergency_kit" value="No"> No<br><br>

    <p><b>Note:</b> If "No" is selected, this household may need priority assistance.</p>

    <label>Evacuation Plan:</label><br>
    <input type="checkbox" name="evacuation" value="Assigned Center"> Assigned Center<br>
    <input type="checkbox" name="evacuation" value="Family Meeting Point"> Family Meeting Point

    <br><br>

    <h3>Past Disaster Experience</h3>

    <textarea name="experience" rows="4" cols="50" placeholder="Describe any past disaster experience..."></textarea>

    <br><br>

    <h3>Location Map</h3>

    <p>Map Integration Placeholder (GIS Data)</p>

    <br>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit Survey">

</form>

<br>

<h2>Printable Report (Manual Copy)</h2>
<p>Barangay officials may print this page and review submitted responses.</p>

</body>
</html>
